Nuremburg 2012 }) (6. Qc2 b5 7. a4 c6 8. Bg2 Bb7 9. O-O O-O 10. b3 c5! (10... c3 11. Nb1 c5 12. Nxc3 { K.Landa-S.Movsesian, Czech Team Championships 2015 }) 11. bxc4 (11. dxc5? c3! 12. Nb1 Be4 $19) 11... bxc4 12. Bb2 (12. dxc5 c3 $15) 12... Bxd2 (12... cxd4!? $146) 13. Qxd2 cxd4 14. Bxd4 Nbd7 15. Rfc1 Bd5 $15 { K.Korley-G.Gajewski, Icelandic Team Championships 2015 }) 6... b5 { [%cal Gc8b7] } 7. O-O O-O { [%cal Ga2a4,Gb2b3] } 8. a4 (8. b3!? c3 { [%cal Gb2b3] } 9. Nb1 Bb7 $132 10. a3?! Be4! $36 { K.Chernyshov-L.
Totsky, Rymarov 1999 } { [%cal Gc3c2] }) 8... c6 9. axb5 cxb5 10. Ng5!? (10. Nh4 Nd5 $7 11. e4 Ne7 12. e5 Nbc6 13. Qg4 Bxd2! 14. Bxd2 Bb7 { =/+/-/+ }) 10... Nd5 11. e4 Nc7 12. Nxh7 Kxh7 13. e5 { K.Troff-M.Zajic, Dallas 2015 } 13... g6! $146 14. Bxa8 Nxa8 15. Qf3 Bd7! $13) 5... Bd6!? { [%cal Rb1d2,Yd1d4] } (5... Be7) 6. Bg2 (6. Nc3!? O-O 7. Bg5 Be7!? $146 (7... c6 8. Bg2 Nbd7?! (8... h6 9. Bxf6 Qxf6 10. O-O $14) 9. e4! dxe4 10. Nxe4 Bb4+ 11. Nc3 h6 12. Bf4!? $14 { Al.Onischuk-D.Naroditsky, US Championships 2015 }) 8. Bg2 Nbd7 9. O-O h6 10. Bxf6 Nxf6 11. Qd3 (11. Qc2 dxc4! 12. Rfd1 c5! 13. dxc5 Qc7) 11... c6 { =/+/= } 12. Rfd1 (12. e4 dxc4!? 13. Qxc4 b5! 14. Qxc6 Rb8! 15. e5? Bb7 16. Qxb5 Bxf3 $19) 12... b6 13. e4 Ba6 14. b3 Qc7 15. e5 Nd7 16. cxd5) 6... c6 7. Qc2 (7. O-O Nbd7 8. b3!? (8. Qc2 O-O { transposes to
the main tabiya }) (8. Nc3 dxc4! 9. e4 e5! { S.Arabi-S.Halkias, Dubai 2011 }) 8... Ne4! 9. Nc3 Nxd2! (9... f5 10. Nxe4 fxe4 11. Ng5 Nf6 12. f3 $14) 10. Qxd2 f5 { M.Andersen-N.Grandelius, European Championships 2015 }) 7... Nbd7 8. O-O O-O { and we've reached the main tabiya. } *


