22. f5! Bf7 (22... exf5 23. Bxd5+ Bf7 24. Bxb7 Rxc1 25. Rxc1 fxg4 26. hxg4 $18) 23. fxe6 Bxe6 24. Rxc8 Rxc8 25. Rc1 Rxc1+ 26. Bxc1 $16 { [%csl Gc1,Gg2,Yd5,Yb6,Yb7,Re6] } 26... Ne5 27. Kf2 Kf7 28. Bb2 Ke7 29. g5! Kd6 30. gxf6 gxf6 { [%csl Rf6,Rh7,Rd5,Rb6,Rb7] } 31. Bd4 Nd7 32. Kg3 Kc6 33. a4! b5? (33... Kd6 34. Kf4 Bf7 35. Bf3 Be6 36. h4 Bf7 37. h5 Be6 (37... h6 38. Kf5 Ke7 39. Bc3 $22 $18) 38. h6 Bf7 39. e4! dxe4 40. Bxe4 $18 { [%cal Ge4h7,Ge4b7] }) 34. a5 $18 { [%csl Yb7,Yb5,Yd5,Yh7,Yf6] } 34... Kd6 35. Kf4 Bf7 36. Bf3 Be6 37. h4 Bh3 38. Bh5 Be6 39. Be8 Bh3 40. Bf7 Bf1 41. Bh5 Bh3 42. Bf3 Be6 43. e4! Bf7 (43... dxe4 44. Bxe4 $18 { [%cal Ge4h7,Ge4b7] }) 44. Bxf6!? Nxf6 45. e5+ Ke6 46. exf6 Kxf6 47. d4 $18 { [%csl Rb7,Rb5,Rd5,Rh7,Ga5,Gb4,Gd4,Gh4] } 47... Be6 48. Be2 Bd7 49. Bd3 h6 50. Be2 Bh3 (50... Bc6 51. Bg4! Be8 $7 (51... Kg6 52. Ke5 $18) 52. Bf5 Bc6 53. Bc8 $22 $18) (50... Ke6 51. Bg4+ Ke7 52. Bxd7 Kxd7 53. Ke5 Kc6 54. h5 $18) 51. Bxb5 Ke6 52. Be2 Kd6 53. b5 Bd7 54. Bd3 Bh3 55. a6 bxa6 56. bxa6 Bd7 57. Bf5 Bb5 58. Bc8 Kc7 59. Bb7 Kb6 60. Ke5 Bc4 61. Kf6 Bd3 62. Kg7 h5 63. Kh6 Be2 64. Bxd5 Kxa6 65. Bf7 Kb5 66. Bxh5 Bd3 67. Bf7 { and Black finally called it quits. } *


